#: Convo.dgn_no_custom_orders_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_no_custom_orders_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.ANSWER_1"
msgid "agent:\n !neutral\n !shocked\n Ugh! Do I look like a bedraggled bard, hat upturnt, kicked-in concertina slung o'er my shoulder? \n player:\n I'm not sure what any of that meant, but the vibe is \"no\". \n agent:\n !disagree\n I. Do. Not. Take. <i>Requests.</>\n !angry\n I am a visionary! A luminary! A... A biggeth deal!\n !gesture\n And thou art lucky to hath the <i>opportunity</> to even glance at my original works.\n !happy\n !closedeyes\n Fortunately for you I am also merciful, so I shall allow you to purchase said works, despite the insultations."
msgstr ""

