#: Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B
msgctxt "Convo.dgn_seen_missing_friends_armorsmith_market.HUB0.convo.giver.STATE_0.QUESTION_2B"
