msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,first_run_in_eggzy_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,first_run_in_eggzy_region,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n !dubious\n What <i>is</> that smell?\n !shocked\n This place stinks like a rotten egg.\n !disagree\n That's disconcerting..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_bow].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_bow].1"
msgid "agent:\n !happy\n !dubious\n Now <i>there's</> a real Hunter's weapon. Sleek, agile, versatile... not to mention incredibly cool-looking.\n player:\n Which of your teammates used the {name.weapon_bow}?\n agent:\n !happy\n !gesture\n That would be yours truly! Figured my old Hunting <#RED>{name.weapon_bow}</> might be useful for training new Hunters.\n !think\n Though I have to admit, it doesn't hold a candle to the fancy <#RED>{name_multiple.weapon_bow}</> you can make nowadays. Who woulda thought one day we'd be using <#RED>{name.rot}</> parts to make our weapons stronger?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_cannon].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_cannon].1"
msgid "!happy\n !think\n Heh. I just remembered the time me and my teammates decided we'd throw <#BLUE>Tommy</> a surprise birthday party.\n !laugh\n In retrospect, probably not the best idea to startle the guy with the <#RED>{name.weapon_cannon}</>. What a mess!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_hammer].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_hammer].1"
msgid "!happy\n !think\n Heh. My old teammate <#BLUE>Nellie</> used to say, 'any problem can be solved with a big enough hammer'.\n !neutral\n !shrug\n ...It was best not to get on her bad side."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_polearm].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_polearm].1"
msgid "agent:\n !happy\n !gesture\n It's a shame you never got to meet <#BLUE>Pike</>. He could make a <#RED>{name.weapon_polearm}</> sail through the air like it was nothing.\n !neutral\n !dejected\n ...But <i>yeesh,</> the constant puns! Always saying stuff like 'I got the point' and 'I'll spearhead the next Hunt'. It was relentless!\n player:\n Sounds like he was pretty sharp. I think we would've gotten along.\n agent:\n !neutral\n !think\n On second thought, it's probably a mercy you two never met."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_shotput].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,friend_npc_dojo_master_is_level_10,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo,weapon_type_shotput].1"
msgid "agent:\n !happy\n !point\n Heh. I remember when <#BLUE>Rover</> first tried to sell me on using a giant ball as a weapon--truth be told, I thought he was nuts.\n !shrug\n But then I saw him in action... took down <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</> like it was child's play, looking like he was having the time of his life. Needless to say, I was convinced.\n player:\n So it <i>is</> a ball!\n agent:\n !neutral\n !point\n ...Hush, you."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_deposited_4_zone_1_hearts,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo]NOT[has_teffrometer].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_deposited_4_zone_1_hearts,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo]NOT[has_teffrometer].1"
msgid "!neutral\n !shocked\n Did ya feel that? There's somethin' strange goin' on out there...\n !point\n Mind checkin' on <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>? They're looking a mite twitchy."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_killed_yammo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,is_wearing_head].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_killed_yammo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,is_wearing_head].1"
msgid "!happy\n !point\n You should really think about getting a helmet, y'know.\n !shrug\n Sorry the expedition didn't provide one."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_killed_yammo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,is_wearing_head].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_killed_yammo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,is_wearing_head].2"
msgid "!neutral\n !think\n You should probably have some head protection.\n !happy\n !shrug\n That was an oversight on my part. Sorry."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_killed_yammo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,is_wearing_head].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_killed_yammo_miniboss,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_megatreemon,is_wearing_head].3"
msgid "!neutral\n !think\n You could probably use a helmet, huh?\n !point\n Maybe you could get one of the forest denizens to sell you one on our next Hunt."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_bandicoot,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_bandicoot,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_bandicoot,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_bandi_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_bandicoot,in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n !dubious\n Just wait 'til that <#RED>{name.bandicoot}</> takes you on head-to-head! To... head? \n !laugh\n Er, we'll see who gets the last laugh."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1"
msgid "!happy\n !point\n You can't make a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_heart}</> omelette without breaking a few eggs.\n !happy\n !angry\n Let's get cracking, Hunter!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n !greet\n Let's get that <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_heart}</>, Hunter!\n !think\n But, um... try not to get any shell bits in it, alright?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].3"
msgid "!happy\n !point\n Don't worry, you've got this.\n !clap\n This fight will be over-easy!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].4"
msgid "!neutral\n !greet\n You know what to do, right Hunter?\n !angry\n Get in there and beat that bad egg!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_eggzy,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].5"
msgid "!happy\n !agree\n This is it.\n !clap\n That oversized <#RED>{name.rot}</> is going to shell out its <#KONJUR>{name.konjur_heart}</>!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n !nervous\n That <#RED>{name.grimhollow}</> really gives me the creeps.\n !closedeyes\n <i>(sigh)</> But we've come too far to back down now."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].2"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n !shrug\n Don't worry about it, Hunter.\n !gruffnod\n You'll get that <#RED>{name.grimhollow}</> next time, I know it!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_grimhollow,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_grimhollow_volcano,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_grimhollow,in_town].3"
msgid "!neutral [keep-for-room]\n !think\n That <#RED>{name.grimhollow}</> is standing between us and finding our answers.\n !angry\n We can't let it win!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_owlitzer,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_owlitzer,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_owlitzer,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_owlitzer_forest,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_owlitzer,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n !nervous\n You promise to take down that <#RED>{name.owlitzer}</>, Hunter?\n !scared\n I hate birds..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_sedament,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_sedament,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].1"
msgid "!neutral\n !think\n If you get cold while fighting <#RED>{name.sedament}</> just um... Think warm thoughts!\n !closedeyes\n Like imagine being next to a warm fire. Mind over matter, right?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_sedament,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_sedament,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].2"
msgid "!happy\n !point\n <#RED>{name.sedament}</> better watch out!\n !angry\n We're comin' for that <#KONJUR>{name.i_konjur_heart}</>!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_sedament,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_sedament,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_sedament_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_sedament,in_town].3"
msgid "!happy\n !point\n Ready to take down <#RED>{name.sedament}</>?\n !agree\n Personally, I think you're ready."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_thatcher,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_thatcher,in_town].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,has_seen_thatcher,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_thatcher_swamp,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_thatcher,in_town].1"
msgid "!agree\n Time to face the music.\n !gesture\n By which I mean a <#RED>{name.rot_boss}</>."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,is_wearing_body,is_wearing_waist,role_scout]NOT[wf_town_has_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,is_wearing_body,is_wearing_waist,role_scout]NOT[wf_town_has_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n !nervous\n Oh boy, your expedition-issued gear isn't cutting it anymore, huh?\n !neutral\n !think\n I'm certain <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> somewhere in the <#RED>{name.treemon_forest}</>.\n !point\n If we can rescue her, she can start <#RED>Upgrading</> your <#RED>Armour</>."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,role_scout,wf_town_has_armorsmith].1"
msgid "!happy\n !think\n Hey Hunter, your <#RED>Armour's</> looking a little outdated.\n !point\n Why don't you give <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}'s</> <#RED>Armour Rack</> a visit and get some <#RED>Upgrades</>?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,role_scout].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,role_scout].1"
msgid "!happy\n !point\n You should think about getting some better protection, now that you're settled in.\n !think\n I remember seeing an <#RED>Armour</> merchant on our last Hunt, now that I think of it."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,role_scout].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,is_wearing_bad_armour,role_scout].2"
msgid "!happy\n !dubious\n Hey Hunter, is that <#RED>Armour</> of yours strong enough...?\n !neutral\n !gesture\n You might want to start buying some new pieces.\n !happy\n !think\n You've seen that odd purple fellow selling <#RED>Armour</> during your Hunts, right?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_yammo_miniboss,role_dojo].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,last_killed_by_yammo_miniboss,role_dojo].1"
msgid "agent:\n !happy\n !dubious\n Judging by those bruises, I'm guessing yer having some trouble taking down a <#RED>{name.yammo_miniboss}</>.\n !point\n The thing you gotta remember is that while a <#RED>{name.yammo_miniboss}</> hits hard, it's also slow to wind up. Keep an eye out for that wind up, and it'll be easier to {name.tutorial_dodge} when it finally swings.\n !gesture\n It's better to <#RED>Dodge</> than run away-- you'll stay in range to land a few <#RED>Attacks</> before the <#RED>{name.yammo_miniboss}</> comes at you again.\n !point\n Plus you'll be <#RED>Invincible</> for a split second during the {name.tutorial_dodge}, so even if you're up close and personal, you won't take any <#RED>Damage</>.\n !shrug\n Just make sure to time it right.\n player:\n Thanks, teach!\n agent:\n !happy\n !agree\n Heh. Go get 'em, Hunter."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_after_insert_heart_scout_owl,role_armorsmith].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_after_insert_heart_scout_owl,role_armorsmith].1"
msgid "agent:\n !neutral\n !shocked\n Did I hear that right? You didn't know <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> is <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}'s</> grandkid?\n player:\n Hey, that was a private conversation!\n agent:\n !happy\n !disagree\n You were talking within earshot of my armoury, that's basically <i>inviting</> me to listen in.\n !happy\n !point\n I don't blame you, though. <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}'s</> so unassuming! \n !think\n It's hard to imagine they're related to <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</>...\n !bliss\n The <i>silver fox</> who invented {name.c_konjur} power... \n !shocked\n Ah! N-now don't tell <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> I said that, okay? This was a private conversation, after all!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_after_insert_heart_scout_owl,role_dojo].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,qc_after_insert_heart_scout_owl,role_dojo].1"
msgid "agent:\n !happy\n !gesture\n So, <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> told you about their famous grandpappy, eh? \n player:\n Do you know anything else about {name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}?\n agent:\n !neutral\n !think\n Well... he was a genius. He personally designed all of <#BLUE>the Rotwood's</> <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}-powered</> infrastructure.\n !disagree\n ...And he never let you forget it. He could be a real pain to work with.\n player:\n <i>You</> worked with {name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}?!\n agent:\n !happy\n !laugh\n Don't get the wrong idea, it wasn't anything science-y. I am and always have been a proud grunt-for-hire.\n !neutral\n !gesture\n ...But yeah. A couple years before the eruption, <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> hired me to train a team. We were responsible for keepin' <#BLUE>the Capital</> free of any wayward <#RED>{name_multiple.rot}</>.\n player:\n Wait... there were {name_multiple.rot} <i>before</> the eruption?\n agent:\n !neutral\n !disagree\n Not many--not like today. I'm not surprised you never heard about them, it was kept real hush-hush. <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> was pretty clear that he didn't wanna worry folks.\n !think\n But every so often one would turn up. We'd get a call about a missing pet, or a garden plot that got torn up, and we'd find a <#RED>{name.rot}</> roamin' the streets.\n !gesture\n <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> said they must've come from the sea, swam over from another continent, and wandered into town.\n player:\n But you have a different theory?\n agent:\n !neutral\n !closedeyes\n ...Yeah. I do. But a gut feeling ain't proof. And it's not like it makes a difference now."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "!happy\n !point\n You beat up an old fox a year ago. Feel good? \n !think\n Everyone feels more settled after you did it.\n !bliss\n And that feels good to me."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "agent:\n !neutral\n !nervous\n The <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>. Makes everything so... quiet.\n !dejected\n No wind. No bugs. No birds... \n !happy\n !gesture\n Sometimes I stand in the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> with my <#KONJUR>Bubble Amulet</>.\n !clap\n Make a little opening, let the wind and bugs and birds in. \n !angry\n <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> yells at me. I don't let <#RED>{name.rot}</> in!\n !closedeyes\n Just enough Wilds in. We need it. To feel connected.\n !disagree\n We can't live in a \"tek-mo-cricket del-oo-shun.\"\n player:\n \"Technocratic delusion\"? Wait... you've been hanging out with {name.npc_refiner}, haven't you?\n agent:\n !happy\n !dubious\n {name.apothecary_sniff} Yes. Do I smell like nerd?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "!happy\n !think\n <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</>. He made the <#KONJUR>Bubble Amulet</>. \n !agree\n He loves <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.gem}</>. My Granny did too. \n !gesture\n She kept a lot of <#KONJUR>{name_multiple.gem}</> around our hut. Told me all about their powers. \n !disagree\n I never believed her. But I can see it now, with the <#KONJUR>Bubble Amulet</>.\n !think\n A lot of things Granny said feel more true now than ever."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_apothecary,super_frenzy_unlocked].4"
msgid "!neutral\n !agree\n Since you beat the old fox. Things have changed.\n !nervous\n When I roam the Wilds now, I actually gotta be careful. \n !think\n <#RED>{name.rot}'s</> changed. Meaner. Smarter, too.\n !closedeyes\n They can see through my invisibilty trick! \n !angry\n {name.apothecary_hiss}\n !point\n Now I have to be regular-sneaky-but-better."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "agent:\n !happy\n !greet\n Hunter! <#BLUE>{name.npc_lunn}</> says since it's been a year, he's ready to congratulate you on beating <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa} {name.flitt_lastname}</> and saving us all. \n player:\n Oh, gee, thanks {name.npc_lunn}!\n agent:\n !agree\n Well, it's from the both of us, but I already thanked you a year ago. I think."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "!happy\n !agree\n Having the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> up and running this past year's made me feel a lot safer. \n !point\n And I have it on good authority most of the camp feels safer too! \n !shrug\n If their diary entries and their just-too-loud conversations are any indication."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "agent:\n !neutral\n !dubious\n Hunter! Have you been ignoring <#BLUE>Cassandra</>? \n player:\n ... \"Cassandra\"? Sorry, but who's \"Cassandra\"?\n agent:\n !shocked\n HUN-<i>TER!</> Keep it down! She'll hear you!\n !gesture\n You know Cassandra. Cassy! Cassafrass! Cassarole! \n !angry\n <z 0.7>The Bubble Shield!</>\n player:\n Huh? Oh! Oh... \"Cassandra\" is what you named the Bubble Shield.\n agent:\n !eyeroll\n She's nearly a year old, so it's important! She'll start recognizing her name any moment now..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_armorsmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].4"
msgid "!neutral\n !nervous\n I wonder how <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}'s</> is doing out in the Wilds these days. \n !eyeroll\n I wish he'd come inside the <#KONJUR>Bubble</> but he'd <i>never.</>\n !shrug\n Bad for his brand, y'know."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "agent:\n !happy\n !agree\n Mm. I'm proud o' the work done to get the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> up. \n !neutral\n !think\n A crumb o' redemption on a table laden with a feast o' regret. \n !happy\n !gruffnod\n But I'll take a crumb. Aye. A crumb'll do."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "!happy\n !agree\n Talented kids, <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</> and <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</> are. \n !think\n Workin' alongside 'em on the ol' <#KONJUR>{name.town_grid_cryst}</>... reminded me o' the old days... \n !gruffnod\n Good ta know this generation takes pride in their work. \n !shrug\n Even ifn I cannae ken the patter comin' out their gobs halfa the time."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "agent:\n !happy\n !greet\n How's yer <#KONJUR>Bubble Amulet</> workin', Hunter? \n player:\n Good! Still letting me pass through the Bubble Shield, no problem.\n agent:\n !gruffnod\n Och. Bein' a Gemologist comes in handy now 'n' again. \n !shrug\n Particularly with <#BLUE>{name.npc_armorsmith}</>, who keeps losin' her <#KONJUR>Bubble Amulet</>.\n !dubious\n Tho I reckon she just wannae gab 'bout romance novels 'n' the like."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith,super_frenzy_unlocked].4"
msgid "agent:\n !neutral\n !disagree\n A year gone by. We're safer, aye, but <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}'s</> in the wind. I dunnae like it. \n !dubious\n Even without <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</> pullin' his strings, <#BLUE>{name.flitt_lastname}</> was a sleekit one. \n !point\n Ye cannae trust the sort, 'specially when cornered. And I'd count this as bein' cornered."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n !shocked\n What, are ye tryin' ta blind me?\n !angry\n Feh."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].2"
msgid "!neutral\n !disagree\n Och! Did <#BLUE>{name.job_armorsmith}</> sell ya \"invisible armour\"?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].3"
msgid "!neutral\n !dubious\n <z 0.7>Psst! Put some clothes on, Hunter. For our sake, at least.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n !dubious\n ...\n !disagree\n <z 0.7>I dinnae even want t'ask.</>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_waist].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_waist].2"
msgid "!neutral\n !eyeroll\n Is this what comedy's come ta?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_waist].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_blacksmith]NOT[is_wearing_waist].3"
msgid "!neutral\n !point\n I ken wantin' ta feel a breeze, but could ya do it <i>away</> from me?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "!happy\n !agree\n Been a year under the big pink bubble and I gotta say, I feel snug as a bug in a rug!\n !bliss\n It's like I'm a shiny lil' jewel, nestled all safe-like in, well, a safe! Locked in tight! \n !neutral\n !scared\n Locked in... like in a... a jail...\n !neutral\n !nervous\n Y'know what, hun? We're just <i>not</> gonna dwell on that. Who wants some grub?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "!happy\n !agree\n The <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> makes me feel safer, sure it does, hun. \n !neutral\n !point\n But don't think I forgot about <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}'s</> Grampy. \n !gruffnod\n I've seen a lot of crooked types try and straighten out, only to spring back to their usual shape...\n !shrug\n It's as they say: once a crook, always a crook...\n !nervous\n Er, well, which isn't <i>always</> true, in <i>every</> case, mind. Who wants some grub?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_cook,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "!neutral\n !gesture\n Chalk it up to my years of leapin' from one, ah, kitchen to another...\n !dubious\n But I ain't never been much fer the feelin' of security. \n !nervous\n Always feels like the other shoe's set to drop, y'know?\n !laugh\n Or in this case, the bubble's set to pop! \n !nervous\n Ah, eh... Anyway... Who wants some grub?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n !dubious\n You uh, testin' a new intimidation tactic?\n !gesture\n {name.dojo_cough}"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo]NOT[is_wearing_waist].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo]NOT[is_wearing_waist].1"
msgid "!neutral\n !dubious\n Err... {name.dojo_cough}\n !point\n You forget to finish dressing this morning?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_dojo_master,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "agent:	\n !happy\n !greet\n If it isn't the hero of the Battle of <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</>. \n player:\n It feels like it <i>just</> happened... \n agent:\n !neutral\n !agree\n Heh. Yeah. That's normal, Hunter. As they write the songs and epic poems, shaping your deeds into jaunty tunes and fancy words...\n !think\n ... we live with the very real memories themselves. They lay in wait around corners, in shadows, in sudden noises--then we're right back there, heart racing and blades flashing.\n !point\n You faced something none of us ever has, Hunter. Remember that. And remember you survived it, and you're here now because of it.\n !gruffnod\n Be proud. Be humble. And be ready. More challenges await. The {name.run} is never over."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "agent:\n !neutral\n !think\n Was it validating to have my read on the beloved <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}</> as a bad guy confirmed? Uh, <i>YEAH.</> \n !shrug\n But it sucked all the same. Especially for <#BLUE>{name.npc_scout}</>.\n player:\n No longer referred to as the \"precious grandchild,\" I see...\n agent:\n !shrug\n Look, I was mad at them. But they're a legit genius in their own right. \n !happy\n !shocked\n The <#RED>{name.damselfly}</>? Running <i>without</> <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>? Amazing. \n !gruffnod\n Makes a good case for a <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</>-free world after all this. \n !neutral\n !think\n If we can put this Primeval genie back in its bottle. And that's a BIG \"if.\""
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "!happy\n !bliss\n Hunter! I'm thinking about starting a punk band!\n !laugh\n The <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield's</> given me some bandwidth--literally. \n !think\n I'm thinkin' <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}</> on percussion. Plays mostly the anvil, but still...\n !shrug\n <#BLUE>{name.npc_dojo_master}</> on strings--mainly the bow. Me on lead guitar, obvs. \n !point\n And I was thinkin'--stay with me--<#BLUE>{name.npc_apothecary}</> on lead vocals!\n !clap\n All that grunting and growling and hissing? She's <i>perfect!</>\n !gruffnod\n Attitude is like 90% of punk music, so I figure this group'll be, like 80% of the way there."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "!happy\n !gesture\n Visited my dad recently. In the year since you took Doc down, the woods've gotten dodgier...\n !shrug\n But my dad seems good! I mean, good as he's been since Doc let <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</> change him.\n !dubious\n I've brought my <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> a couple times. And his <#KONJUR>{name.konjur}</> signature, it shares a similar frequency to the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>...\n !think\n Probably why the <#RED>{name.rot}</> leaves him alone. \n !neutral\n !dejected\n Needs more research, but... It's hard to see him sometimes, so I gotta space out my visits, y'know?"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_refiner,super_frenzy_unlocked].4"
msgid "!neutral\n !dubious\n I've been thinkin', my dad's connected to <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</>, but still I don't know why it doesn't possess him like it did <#BLUE>Doc {name.flitt_lastname}</>.\n !think\n It's like the connection's reversed. My dad is connected <i>to</> it, plugged into its chaotic, creative <#KONJUR>Teffressence</>, without letting its consciousness flow back into him...\n !notebook\n If only I could find a way for him to shut that connection off--if even temporarily..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].1
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].1"
msgid "!happy\n !gesture\n Looking up at the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</> at night... it almost looks like pink stars twinkling, doesn't it? \n !neutral\n !closedeyes\n Still, I can't help but wonder about the <i>real</> stars, twinkling somewhere beyond it..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].2"
msgid "!happy\n !clap\n Thanks to <#BLUE>{name.npc_blacksmith}'s</> <#KONJUR>Bubble Amulets</> mounted into the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> body, we soar straight through the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>!\n !bliss\n And the <#KONJUR>Amulets</> dampen my allergies, too! I keep one on me at all times, now-ow-AOH-AH--\n !shocked\n AH-<i>CHOO!!</>\n !neutral\n !dubious\n That was just pollen. I think."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].3
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].3"
msgid "agent:\n !happy\n !notebook\n Nearly a year of the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>, and it's holding strong, thanks to you and the team of course...\n player:\n How was it, working with <#BLUE>{name.npc_refiner}</>?\n agent:\n !dejected\n It was hard at first. Her father's madness was caused by <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}</>... on <i>my</> account. \n !gesture\n But after pouring our blood, sweat, and tears into the the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>, the resentment, confusion, and strangeness--it all melted away. \n !gruffnod\n We're bonded as scientists now, and friends. We're now tuning her <#KONJUR>{name.teffrometer}</> with <#KONJUR>Primeval {name.konjur}</> she stole from the lab.\n !think\n With it, we hope to find some way to cure her father, and maybe even cure my... maybe even cure <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}</>. Someday."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].4
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].4"
msgid "agent:\n !happy\n !gesture\n Hunter. It's hard to express my thanks for all you've done for us. \n !gruffnod\n You've put your life on the line day-in, day-out for our quest to make a better world. \n !think\n Defeating <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}</>, stopping the <#KONJUR>Second Eruption</>, fueling the <#KONJUR>Bubble Shield</>...\n !closedeyes\n I hesitate to think where we'd be without you.\n player:\n Of course, {name.npc_scout}. But it's given me purpose. That's gift enough. \n agent:\n !shocked\n A-a gift? Oh dear, I... I wasn't building up to a gift. Just saying thank you. \n player:\n Oh! Oh. I'm sorry. Wow. I'm really embarrassed. \n agent:\n !laugh\n Oh my... well thanks for all you've done, including making this awkward, Hunter!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].5
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].5"
msgid "!neutral\n !gesture\n This scarf belonged to my... to <#BLUE>{name.npc_grandpa}</>. \n !think\n In the year since we last saw him, I kept wearing it--out of habit, I suppose. But the hurt, betrayal, and anger lingered...\n !dubious\n I've wanted to throw it away so many times.  \n !closedeyes\n But I couldn't. \n !gesture\n Perhaps this old scarf is a reminder of my hope--threadbare as it is--that he'll come back to himself, and come back to us.\n !shrug\n Is that naive? Foolish? Maybe. Or maybe it's the same hope that keeps me fighting for our future.  \n !gruffnod\n And we must hold onto hope--even if it's in tatters. Especially so. I believe that to my core."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].6
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout,super_frenzy_unlocked].6"
msgid "!happy\n !greet\n Hello, Hunter. Or should I say, \"The Hero of the Battle of <#BLUE>{name.tefframech_volcano}</>\"! \n !clap\n I hear your legend's even spread to <#BLUE>The Brinks</>!\n !point\n Rousing people from their torpor to join the <#RED>{name_multiple.foxtails}</> in our epic quest!\n !laugh\n I even hear <#BLUE>{name.npc_market_merchant}</> is selling anniversary edition brown cloaks!"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].1
