#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].2"
msgid "!neutral\n !point\n I don't think you're going to enjoy the <#RED>{name.i_damselfly}</> ride dressed like that.\n !dubious\n There's a lot of wind up there..."
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_body,is_wearing_head,is_wearing_waist].3
