#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_waist].2
msgctxt "Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,in_town,role_scout]NOT[is_wearing_waist].2"
msgid "!neutral\n !shocked\n Ah! Um. Hunter?\n !happy\n !nervous\n Would you mind putting on some pants, please?"
