msgid "!neutral\n !gesture\n Okay, okay. This is serious. I promise I'm out of egg yolks.\n !shocked\n Egg jokes! I meant to say egg jokes!\n !dejected\n Err... sorry.\n !angry\n <z 0.7>Come on {name.npc_scout}, get it together! You're better than this!</z>"
msgstr ""

#: Quest.chat_fluff_fallback.QUIP.chitchat:[chitchat,in_quest_chat_fluff_fallback,location_eggzy_tundra,role_scout]NOT[has_killed_eggzy,in_town].1
