msgctxt "Quest.twn_repeatable_tutorials_dojo.TUTORIALS.REWARD_TIER_TWO.TALK"
msgid "!happy\n !dubious\n That's what, three lessons you've done now? Yer rocketing up my ranking list, kid.\n !neutral\n !agree\n And yes, I keep a mental ranking of all my students."
